    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>(S) In Dei omnipotentis nomine amen. Breve ad futuri temporis
                        demonstrationem qualiter hoc actum est <placeName ref="#places/4"
                            >Luce</placeName> in domo <persName key="#Witness #Judge"><name
                                ref="Rodelandus">Rolandi</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Judge">iudicis</rs>
                        <persName><name ref="Guarmignanus">Guamignani</name></persName>, que est
                            <placeName ref="#places/4">ubi dicitur Curtis Regia</placeName>, bonorum
                        virorum presentia nomina quorum denotabuntur in subiectis. <persName><name
                                ref="Bartholomaeus">Bartholomeus</name></persName> filius
                                <persName><name ref="Corsus">Corsi</name></persName> atque
                                <persName><name ref="Lucia">Lucia</name></persName> iugalis eius et
                        filia quondam <persName><name ref="Bertolottus"
                        >Bertolotti</name></persName>, consensu viri et notitia Rolandi iudicis
                        quondam Guamignani, ambo insimul fecerunt finem, refutationem atque
                        transationem de quattuor lib. capitale et earum usuris quas quondam
                                <persName><name ref="Laborator">Laboratore</name></persName>
                        <persName><name ref="Farulfus">Ferolfi</name></persName> debebat quondam
                                <persName><name ref="Aimerigus">Aimerigo</name></persName> filio
                        quondam <persName><name ref="Martinus">Martini</name></persName> uterino
                        fratre suprascripte Lucie, unde obligaverat ei mediam cultram terre loco
                            <placeName ref="#places/633" key="#Churches">Scheto</placeName> que est
                        campus et ortus simul prope <rs key="#Churches">ecclesia</rs>
                        <orgName key="#Churches" ref="#juridical_persons/3112">Sancti
                            Iohannis</orgName> sicut continetur in carta inde scripta manu <persName
                            key="#Notary"><name ref="Ciprianus">Cipriani</name></persName> notarii.
                        Et hoc fecerunt in manu <persName key="#Advocatus"><name ref="Savinus"
                                >Savini</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Advocatus">advocati</rs>
                        <orgName key="#Hospitals" ref="#juridical_persons/3206"><rs key="#Hospitals"
                                >hosspitalis</rs> de <placeName ref="#places/3207" key="#Hospitals"
                                >Altepascio</placeName></orgName> (…) pro <persName><name
                                ref="Dominicus">Domnico</name></persName> rectore ipsius
                        hosspitalis. (…) Professi sunt suprascripti iugales recepisse <rs
                            key="#Meritum/launechild">meritum a suprascripto Savino lib. sex
                            lucensium denariorum</rs>. <foreign>Pena</foreign>: mille sol. lucensium
                        denariorum et consulum et treguanorum lucensium presentium et futurorum vel
                        alterius potestatis que Lucam distringetur. (…) Hec acta sunt <rs
                            key="#Witness">presentia</rs> suprascripti Rolandi iudicis, <persName
                            key="#Witness #Causidicus"><name ref="Tiniosus"
                            >Tiniosi</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Causidicus">causidici</rs>, <persName key="#Witness"><name
                                ref="Rainerius">Raineri</name></persName> filii Corsi atque
                            <persName key="#Witness"><name ref="Genovese">Genovesi</name></persName>
                        quondam Bertolotti et aliorum. Anno dominice nativitatis millesimo centesimo
                        octuagesimo tertio, octavo kalendas martii, indictione prima. </ab> <ab>Preterea <persName key="#Notary"><name ref="Wilielmus">Guilielmus</name></persName> notarius
                        quondam <persName><name ref="Heinricus/Pedrectus">Arigi
                            Pedretti</name></persName>, rogatu suprascripti Bartholomei, fideiussit
                        pro eius et sollepni stipulatione promisit (…) quod si de predicto capitale
                        et earum usuris vel ipsa obligatione seu pingnore (…) ipsum dictum hospitale
                        vel cui dederit aut aliqua persona pro eo danum vel menumantia habuerit,
                        quod emendaberat infra triginta dies, ex quo inquisitus fuerit. (…) Hoc
                        actum est in eodem loco altera die, coram predicto Rolando iudice atque
                            <persName key="#Witness"><name ref="Tado">Tadolino</name></persName>
                        quondam <persName><name ref="Nontigiova">Nontigiove</name></persName> et
                        ipso Bartholomeo cuius rogatu hoc fecit. (…) <persName key="#Writer #Notary"
                                ><name ref="Hubertus">Ubertus</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Notary">notarius</rs> domni imperatoris his omnibus interfui et
                        hec ad memorie casam (sic) <rs key="#Writer">descripsi</rs>.</ab>
                </div>
